This paper is about developing a dialogue system that can automatically infer the topic of a conversation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). The use of deep learning techniques and self attention also suggests a focus on machine learning and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SD (Sound), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
